/* ESP32-CAM Image Capture for Edge Impulse Training
 *
 * This sketch creates a web interface to capture images
 * for training your Edge Impulse model.
 *
 * Usage:
 * 1. Upload this code to ESP32-CAM
 * 2. Open Serial Monitor to get the IP address
 * 3. Go to http://<IP_ADDRESS> in your browser
 * 4. Click "Capture" to take photos
 * 5. Right-click captured images to save
 * 6. Upload images to Edge Impulse Studio
 */

